        <abstract> 
<p>Remarks on fossils described in A. D. d’Orbigny’s <hi rend="italic">Voyage dans l’Amérique méridionale</hi>.</p>  
<p>Asks CL whether he has talked with John Murray concerning 2d ed. [of <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Mentions conversation with Hugh Cuming about South American shells. Has had G. B. Sowerby (elder) look at some specimens.</p>
        </abstract>
